title: The Rockets OOP Albums: No Ballads, The Rockets (TurnUp The Radi
description:
The Rockets were a band from Detroit in the late 70&#039;s and early 80&#039;s.  They recorded 5 studio albums and one live album.  To date, these are the only albums not yet released onto cd.  These albums were recorded from pristine albums and pops and clicks were removed using cool edit pro.
